Option A ‚Äî Bakta (modern, best for bacterial WGS)

If you want the most accurate and curated annotation (recommended):

1. Install Bakta
conda install -c conda-forge -c bioconda bakta

mkdir -p bakta_db
bakta_db download --type light --output bakta_db

Bakta‚Äôs light database (~1.5 GB) is small , it contains curated, high-quality biological datasets used for accurate genome annotation.
